    <item>
      <title>印度季风降雨充沛将促进经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度预测今年的季风将高于正常水平，人们乐观地认为充足的降雨将刺激农作物产量和经济增长，并促使政府放松对小麦、大米和食糖出口的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行 Simkus 预计 2024 年将降息三次，有可能第四次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ecb-s-simkus-sees-three-rate-cuts-this-year-chance-of-fourth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员格迪米纳斯·西姆库斯表示，借贷成本将从 6 月开始下降——预计 2024 年至少会发生三起此类举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/ecb-s-simkus-sees-three-rate-cuts-this-year-chance-of-fourth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 07:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯表示，随着中国紧张局势升级，死亡可能触发美国协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/marcos-says-no-plans-to-grant-us-access-to-more-military-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在与中国关系日益紧张的情况下表示，如果一名菲律宾士兵死于外国袭击，菲律宾将援引与美国的防务条约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/marcos-says-no-plans-to-grant-us-access-to-more-military-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:52:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场押注紧张局势缓和，以色列谢克尔反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/israeli-shekel-gains-as-traders-watch-response-to-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者押注伊朗和以色列之间的冲突不会进一步升级，以色列货币在一轮抛售后反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/israeli-shekel-gains-as-traders-watch-response-to-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于交易员再次关注通胀风险，美国国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末前席卷市场的国债买盘正在平息，人们希望伊朗和以色列之间的冲突现在能够平息，人们的注意力又回到了困扰世界经济的通胀压力上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:26:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗紧张局势缓和，石油稳定，国债下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一全球市场平静，交易员猜测外交努力将有助于防止伊朗和以色列之间的冲突升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</guid>
